Coding is hard, let AI help Features AI can infer the most relevant method you are calling, and rank it first in autocomplete list Tell AI by writing a line of intention such as /// convert myString to int , Enter, AI will fill in the code snippet for you. ... more to come Notes You will also need to the AI.codes dashboard (in fact a local proxy) for this plugin to be functional. The local proxy ensures good user experience by talking to server asynchronously, as retrieving candidates from server usually takes more than 100ms, causing visible delay in UI. This feature is still in early alpha, and it can break, burn, or make your eyes itchy.
